                                        | Food was delicious. We had the Caesar salad and balsamic salad. So good ! Then we had a pizza and the lasagna which came with the house salad. All salads were very good. The lasagna was great and rich. We had to take food home! The restaurant is owned by a mother and daughter and it&rsquo;s in the garden of the mom&rsquo;s house. Great food, great people and unique concept! We will be back!
