                                        | Charming little family owned courtyard restaurant serving pasta, pizza and steak. The atmosphere is cute and cozy! We started with the bruschetta which was caprese style and delicious! My husband enjoyed the lasagna and I had a medium rare steak that was cooked perfectly, followed by an after dinner sangria and delicious flan for dessert! All homemade by a mother and daughter co-owner duo! Although we didn&rsquo;t try the pizza, we overheard a group sitting next to us say it was one of the best pizzas they&rsquo;ve ever had! Highly recommend this little unexpected gem!
